{
  "texts": [
    "Not only do tasks associated with NLG require retrieval enhancement techniques, but NLU tasks also necessitate external information.",
    "To date, there is a scarcity of comprehensive surveys that thoroughly review the application of augmented retrieval techniques across the spectrum of NLP.",
    "In order to improve the current situation, this paper presents the following contributions:",
    "(1) The article does not merely focus on the work related to RAG; it also places significant emphasis on RALM and aligns with the concept of NLP.",
    "The work related to generation aligns with NLG, while the rest of the work aligns with NLU."
  ]
}